{"tid":2431020,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大埔港鐵站11人非法集結案 控方無片呈堂惹官質疑：冇閉路電視點證明？","createTime":"2021-03-03T10:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T14:04:19.000Z","uid":56115,"like":128,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"feada5831c87bad9545ecd1f7528b13ea810f2e3","tid":2431020,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:46:02.000Z","msg":"約200名大埔街坊前年9月7日計劃在港鐵站手拖手築人鏈，聲援機場「和你飛」行動。當晚有市民被指在站內聚集，因而被捕，當中11人事隔一年後遭警方重新拘捕及起訴，控以11項非法集結罪。案件今午在西九龍裁判法院再訊，全部被告不認罪。<span class=\"red\">控方告知法庭將傳召16名警員作供，但沒有影片呈堂</span>。主任裁判官徐綺薇聞言立即質疑謂：「冇可能嘅事啦係咪呀？冇閉路電視，點證明？」主控解釋，由於片段質素較差，故無意呈堂。<br />\n<br />\n徐官再確認，控方所有辨認被告身份的證據均依賴16名警員的證供，對此語帶驚訝謂：「冇可能嘅事啦係咪呀？冇閉路電視，點證明？」"},{"pid":"11a5a1631ee33a28a0096adf38a6d3a71f00dfff","tid":2431020,"uid":56115,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:46:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/6DNGCHAY4ZBKREP4UAIX4WBVQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2F6DNGCHAY4ZBKREP4UAIX4WBVQA%2F&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=c50ab392\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210303%2F6DNGCHAY4ZBKREP4UAIX4WBVQA%2F&h=803cd090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210303/6DNGCHAY4ZBKREP4UAIX4WBVQA/</a>"},{"pid":"222ad8ee2d9b0dee0ee4d29fc1508667c3429d48","tid":2431020,"uid":361975,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:46:59.000Z","msg":"Popo:我對狗眼就係證據"},{"pid":"aba5da574d9754f438e7faf74aebc64bc9ec2f10","tid":2431020,"uid":21545,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"淫審處又多一個官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9854b1b9a72fac8d9534168c46073121aeb37770","tid":2431020,"uid":230530,"like":22,"dislike":7,"score":15,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:50:25.000Z","msg":"佢地好彩 比個清官審"},{"pid":"18a128b788